  <p class="center">
  Football or also known as soccer is without a doubt, the most popular sport in the world. 43% of the world population identifies themselves as soccer fans and 250 million
people play the game. This is due to the impressive dribbling, shooting, and many other skills that these players show off that makes it so entertaining. Another fact is that
the game is cheap to play. You onlyneed a round ball and an open space to play. That is why it is called the "people's game". This saying comes from England which is where football was invented.</p>
